text: Aisling O'Neill is an Irish actress. She has portrayed Carol Foley in Fair City for more than two decades. O'Neill's portrayal of Carol earns her personal letters of admiration and bought her an IFTA nomination for Best Female Performance in a Soap or Comedy. Originally from Dublin, O'Neill lives in Gorey, County Wexford.
